<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Wedding Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      background: #fdf6f0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .card {
      width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 2px solid #d4a373;
      border-radius: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #b56576;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #355070;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #333;
    }
    .date {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #6d597a;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Wedding Invitation</h1>
    <h2>johny and emaily</h2>
    <p>We joyfully invite you to celebrate our union</p>
    <p class="date">On March 20, 2026<br>At Rose Garden, Agra</p>
    <div class="footer">“Two souls, one heart.”</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
